<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 09:16:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着特朗普总统任期的临近，中国市场下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-markets-drop-trump-presidency-looms-2024-11-06/</link><description>由于唐纳德·特朗普再次当选总统以及共和党控制美国国会的前景可能导致贸易和技术方面的紧张局势加剧，中国人民币和股市周三大幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 08:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-markets-drop-trump-presidency-looms-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>博塔斯和周将在赛季结束后离开索伯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/bottas-zhou-leave-sauber-end-season-2024-11-06/</link><description>一级方程式车队周三表示，芬兰车手瓦尔特利·博塔斯和中国车手周冠宇将在赛季结束后离开索伯。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 08:37:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/bottas-zhou-leave-sauber-end-season-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>英国命令中国注册公司出售苏格兰芯片公司股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/uk-orders-china-registered-firm-sell-stake-scottish-chip-company-2024-11-06/</link><description>英国政府周三以国家安全风险为由，责令在中国注册的未来科技设备国际控股有限公司出售苏格兰芯片公司 FTDI 80.2% 的股份。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 08:17:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/uk-orders-china-registered-firm-sell-stake-scottish-chip-company-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国小鹏汽车押注增程混合动力技术以提高销量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xpeng-bets-extended-range-hybrid-tech-boost-sales-2024-11-06/</link><description>小鹏汽车周三推出了增程式混合动力技术，这家中国电动汽车制造商押注于转向此类比纯电动汽车更具成本竞争力的产品，以提高销量并提高盈利能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 08:03:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xpeng-bets-extended-range-hybrid-tech-boost-sales-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>Pandora 2024 年营业利润增长目前处于指导范围的上限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pandora-q3-operating-profit-slightly-below-expectations-2024-11-06/</link><description>全球最大的珠宝制造商丹麦潘多拉 (Pandora) 周三表示，预计今年的营业利润增长将达到预测范围的上限，而其公布的季度营业利润略低于预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pandora-q3-operating-profit-slightly-below-expectations-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国销售疲软和刹车问题，宝马利润大幅下滑，未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-reports-drop-earnings-related-china-brake-issues-2024-11-06/</link><description>宝马周三报告称，由于中国销量下滑和刹车问题，第三季度利润下降61%，低于分析师预期，但表示有望实现调整后的全年财务前景。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:32:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-reports-drop-earnings-related-china-brake-issues-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>尽管中国市场疲软，西门子医疗仍实现年度销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/siemens-healthineers-meets-full-year-earnings-forecast-2024-11-06/</link><description>德国医疗技术公司西门子医疗 (Siemens Healthineers) 周三公布的收入增长和全年调整后息税前利润 (EBIT) 与预期相符，尽管中国市场持续疲软。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:09:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/siemens-healthineers-meets-full-year-earnings-forecast-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>联合国表示，阿富汗鸦片种植在禁令两年后出现反弹并发生变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/afghan-opium-cultivation-bounces-shifts-two-years-after-ban-un-says-2024-11-06/</link><description>联合国周三发布的一份报告称，阿富汗长期以来是全球海洛因原材料的主要供应国，自塔利班禁止鸦片罂粟以来，该国的罂粟产量在第二个整年增长了五分之一，但仍仅是禁令前水平的一小部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:35:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/afghan-opium-cultivation-bounces-shifts-two-years-after-ban-un-says-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：“特朗普交易”如火如荼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-06/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:33:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>台英举行新一轮贸易谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-britain-hold-new-round-trade-talks-2024-11-06/</link><description>官员周三表示，台湾和英国将于本周举行新一轮贸易谈判，重点讨论投资和绿色能源。此前，台北希望去年达成一项协议，以促进这家科技巨头的全球参与。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-britain-hold-new-round-trade-talks-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>受生产困境影响，丰田两年来首次季度利润下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-posts-20-drop-q2-operating-profit-2024-11-06/</link><description>丰田汽车周三公布两年来首次季度利润下降，原因是日本和美国两个关键市场的销售和生产问题疲软，阻碍了这家日本汽车制造商最近创纪录的增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-posts-20-drop-q2-operating-profit-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国国家机密泄露导致前雇员罕见被判死刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-state-secrets-leak-prompts-rare-death-sentence-ex-employee-2024-11-06/</link><description>中国国家安全部周三表示，一名为中国国家机构工作的前雇员因泄露“国家机密”而被罕见地判处死刑，此前他被指控将自己的 USB 驱动器交给外国间谍机构。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-state-secrets-leak-prompts-rare-death-sentence-ex-employee-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，由于天气好转和折扣，10月份中国出口增长可能加快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-export-growth-likely-picked-up-speed-oct-better-weather-discounts-2024-11-06/</link><description>尽管制造商和其他主要出口商报告全球需求下降，但受天气好转和大幅折扣的推动，中国 10 月份的出口量可能会以更快的速度增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 04:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-export-growth-likely-picked-up-speed-oct-better-weather-discounts-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚情报局长表示，俄罗斯和中国的“新兴轴心”令人不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-emerging-axis-troubling-says-australia-intelligence-chief-2024-11-06/</link><description>澳大利亚国家情报办公室负责人表示，包括中国、伊朗和朝鲜在内的向俄罗斯提供支持的国家“新兴轴心”是“令人深感不安的战略发展”，西方国家正在努力追赶。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 01:24:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-china-emerging-axis-troubling-says-australia-intelligence-chief-2024-11-06/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，由于对中国和通胀的担忧，日本制造商11月信心下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-manufacturers-less-confident-november-worries-over-china-inflation-2024-11-05/</link><description>路透社周三的月度调查显示，日本制造商对 11 月份商业状况的信心低于 10 月份，原因是中国经济放缓和持续高通胀削弱了市场情绪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:12:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-manufacturers-less-confident-november-worries-over-china-inflation-2024-11-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>